ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
"enables you to easily prepare and submit an 'Nomination Packet' for many of the organized employee awards that are offered to Hines VA staff to recognize outstanding behaviour, actions, dedication, or other positive impacts on the facility's Veterans, visitors, or other staff.

By answering simple questions in this app, your responses will be pre-populated for you into the correct places for each of the unique types of award. After submission, your packet will automatically be routed to the appropriate 'Award Subcommittee' team for consideration, and you will recieve updates from the Chatbot in Teams about your packet's status."
